GenomeSize

Readdepth.sh
	F: Calculating read depth from bam files
	O: Readdepth/*bed.gz
	
Readdepth.CI.pl
	F: Calculating mean and confidence intervals of the read depth for each sample
	O: Readdepth/CI.txt

Readdepth.vis.R
	F: The identification of sex and the visualization from above
	O: Readdepth.pdf
	
Sex.vis.R	
	F: The visualization of assembly sizes according to the sex
	O: Sex.pdf

selfalign.minimap2/j*
	F: executation of minimap2 for self-alignment
	O: selfalign/paf/*paf.gz
			
selfalign.dupl.pl
	F: identification of self-dupilcated regions
	O: selfalign/dupl.txt

			

